name: Ginger Bread House Vest
description: Don't try and eat this when your drunk. It may look delicious but it's not edible.

name: Stupid Mittens
description:
This just brings me back to those childhood memories of ice skating, wreaths and those stupid mittens that prevents you from zipping your jacket or picking your nose... damn you mittens!

(by Classic Elements. 45% cotton, 55% ramie)

name: Purple "Trees"??
description:
All us elves got drunk one day, and one drank himself colorblind and found this sweater and thought it looked like a bunch of trees.  Don't worry, he now shoveling the reindeer stalls.  But we still have to sell the thing.

(70% acrylic, 30% cotton; by Serious Affairs)

name: Cat Threw Up Flowers
description:
Pointsettas are poisonous, and one of Mrs. Clauses cats nibbled on some and just hurled it all up on this sweater.  Don't worry, its clean... just ugly.

(by Tiara; 45%cotton 55% ramie)

name: BUILT IN SCARF!
description:
Title says it all, it has a scarf that's attached to the top of the sweater, on top of that its got 4 annoying happy snowmen... I mean what they hell are they so happy about, they only live a couple months max, then they literally melt to death or the neighborhood bully comes by with his stupid hockey stick and decapitates him...and then he makes fun of your poofy jacket that you can't even move in... Sniff... Hypothetically speaking.

(by Dress Barn. 55% ramie, 45% cotton)
